        All programs include job placement assistance and industry certifications.
      </p>
      
      <div class="programs-grid">
        <div class="program-card">
          <div class="program-title">Medical Assistant Certification</div>
          <p style="color: #666; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            Comprehensive training in clinical and administrative medical procedures
          </p>
          <div class="program-stats">
            <div class="program-stat">
              <div class="program-stat-number">12 weeks</div>
